lot of the agencies will have demo reels of their

00:34:46.856 --> 00:34:51.641
actors that they represent, and then you can go on
and listen to what the demos should sound like,

00:34:51.641 --> 00:34:54.278
but you'll want to send out to agencies in order
to--

00:34:54.278 --> 00:35:01.197
SAM: Voicebank.net. That has everyone's reel that
you've ever heard. It has all their demo reels,

00:35:01.197 --> 00:35:06.078
you just have to find them. And also, you can buy
Yuri Lowenthal and Tara Platt--

00:35:06.078 --> 00:35:07.467
